(61, 1, '2014-10-22 12:08:33', '2014-10-22 09:08:33', '<a href="http://wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/gear_team_420.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-143 aligncenter" src="http://wp.local/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/gear_team_420-300x203.png" alt="team" width="300" height="203" /></a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Our growing team comes from diverse backgrounds, but two important characteristics we look for in team members are the potential to become the best at what you do and the desire to keep improving towards that. </em><em>If you''re interested in learning, thinking about hard problems and being proud of the difference you''ll make in the world, we hope you''ll join us!</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>', 'Team', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'team', '', '', '2014-10-23 15:04:11', '2014-10-23 12:04:11', '', 56, 'http://wp.local/?page_id=61', 0, 'page', '', 0),
